**Structured Logging with Pino**:
```typescript
// Log levels and format
const logger = pino({
  level: process.env.LOG_LEVEL || 'info',
  formatters: {
    level: (label) => ({ level: label }),
    log: (object) => ({
      ...object,
      timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),
      service: 'ultra-platform',
      version: process.env.APP_VERSION
    })
  }
});
```

